[02:14.76]LAUNCELOT	Sola! did you see Master Lorenzo?
[02:17.49]	Master Lorenzo, sola, sola!
[02:19.72]LORENZO	Leave hollaing, man: here.
[02:21.87]LAUNCELOT	Sola! where? where?
[02:23.53]LORENZO	Here.
[02:24.32]LAUNCELOT	Tell him there's a post come from my master, with
[02:28.27]	his horn full of good news: my master will be here
[02:32.30]	ere morning.
