[02:38.48]	And yet no matter: why should we go in?
[02:41.64]	My friend Stephano, signify, I pray you,
[02:44.80]	Within the house, your mistress is at hand;
[02:48.25]	And bring your music forth into the air.
[02:51.56]	[Exit Stephano]
[02:52.42]	How sweet the moonlight sleeps upon this bank!
[02:56.16]	Here will we sit and let the sounds of music
[02:59.82]	Creep in our ears: soft stillness and the night
[03:03.63]	Become the touches of sweet harmony.
