[06:36.81]PORTIA	Go in, Nerissa;
[06:38.25]	Give order to my servants that they take
[06:41.63]	No note at all of our being absent hence;
[06:45.00]	Nor you, Lorenzo; Jessica, nor you.
[06:47.73]	[A tucket sounds]
[06:48.60]LORENZO	Your husband is at hand; I hear his trumpet:
[06:52.12]	We are no tell-tales, madam; fear you not.
[06:55.42]PORTIA	This night methinks is but the daylight sick;
[06:59.09]	It looks a little paler: 'tis a day,
