[10:44.13]NERISSA	Nor I in yours
[10:45.64]	Till I again see mine.
[10:47.65]BASSANIO	Sweet Portia,
[10:49.01]	If you did know to whom I gave the ring,
[10:52.32]	If you did know for whom I gave the ring
[10:55.70]	And would conceive for what I gave the ring
[10:59.29]	And how unwillingly I left the ring,
